round-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Health and safety</h4><p>Advice and defence in investigations, enforcement action, and prosecutions. We help you manage risk, protect reputation, and demonstrate compliance.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Food safety</h4><p>Support with inspections, investigations, and allegations of non-compliance. Clear guidance to help you respond effectively and protect your business.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Fire safety</h4><p>Practical advice on regulatory duties and representation where enforcement action arises. We help minimise disruption and safeguard continuity.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Housing regulation</h4><p>Support for landlords, developers, and managing agents facing regulatory scrutiny or enforcement proceedings.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Planning enforcement</h4><p>Advice and representation relating to breaches of planning control and enforcement notices. Focused on protecting commercial interests.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Trading law</h4><p>Guidance on consumer protection, unfair trading and regulatory compliance to reduce exposure and support confident decision making.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Environmental law</h4><p>Advice on environmental obligations, investigations and enforcement action. Helping you respond proactively and manage reputational risk.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Care sector regulation</h4><p>Support for care providers facing inspections, regulatory intervention or compliance concerns.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Fraud and tax investigations</h4><p>Strategic advice and representation during investigations involving alleged financial wrongdoing or HMRC scrutiny. We help you respond clearly and confidently, protect your reputation, and minimise disruption while managing risk and maintaining commercial stability.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.9