ht-semibold\">Blacks Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Blacks to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Great communication, understanding, support, Knowledge. We keep coming back as well trusted.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very professional, excellent communication and seamless and quick service...Highly Recommended. Thank you!</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very prompt friendly service - Blacks Solicitors get things completed rapidly and smoothly, friendly staff.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Would highly recommend - they handled our sale with great professionalism and patience. They responded to any request within a timely manner.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Blacks Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"